text: Nataliya Kyshchuk (original name: Наталія Кищук; Also written as: Natalya Kishchuk or Наталья Кищук; born 27 May 1968) is a road cyclist from Ukraine. She competed at 1992 Summer Olympics without representing a nation as part of the Unified Team in the women's road race.
